==== Community Labs ====
[[Special:MyLanguage/Community Labs|Community Labs]] worlds display a notice and warning when joining.

<gallery mode="packed">
File:CommunityLabsLoadingScreen.png|Community Labs
</gallery>

==== Custom ====
Select worlds can display a custom loading screen, needing permission from VRChat. This is usually associated with linking data with a third-party website. This type of loading screen requires the user to press an "Accept & Continue" button to join the world. 

<gallery mode="packed">
File:LoadingScreenCustom_CatsUdon TRPG.png|Custom
</gallery>

